ption":"有机磷农药在短期内大量进入人体，引起病人出现烟碱样症状、中枢神经系统症状等，烟碱样症状主要是横纹肌运动神经末梢过度兴奋所致，表现为肌束震颤，而后发展为呼吸肌麻痹引起周围性呼吸衰竭。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswZ0016_ay_2049_201304","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"心力衰竭","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"肾衰竭","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"DIC","fourth":"肝功能衰竭","answerPic":"","first":"呼吸衰竭"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"瞳孔缩小最常见于","discription":"有机磷农药中毒的病人出现呼出气有大蒜味，瞳孔缩小呈针尖样，腺体分泌增多，肌纤维颤动，大汗淋漓和意识障碍等中毒表现；阿托品中毒时瞳孔散大；深昏迷病人瞳孔散大，对光反射消’失；视神经萎缩表现不同程度的瞳孔散大；视网膜脱落主要是视力的急剧下降，瞳孔可无变化。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswZ0016_ay_2050_201304","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"阿托品中毒","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"深昏迷病人","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"视网膜脱落","fourth":"视神经萎缩","answerPic":"","first":"有机磷农药中毒"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"有机磷农药中毒程度的检查是","discription":"全血胆碱酯酶活力测定是诊断有机磷农药中毒和判断中毒程度、治疗效果和判断预后的依据。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswZ0016_ay_2051_201304","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"碳氧血红蛋白测定","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"残留农药测定","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"胆碱酯酶活力测定","fourth":"神经靶酯酶","answerPic":"","first":"血清丙氨酸转移酶"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"有机磷农药口服中毒，出现症状的时间是","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggswZ0016_ay_2052_201304","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"可在10分钟至2小时内","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"可在10分钟至3小时内","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"可在10分钟至5小时内","fourth":"可在10分钟至4小时内","answerPic":"","first":"可在10分钟至1小时内"},{